tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE ml_model_results (
    result_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    cleaned_data_id UUID,
    model_name VARCHAR,
    accuracy FLOAT,
    prediction_results JSON
);

CREATE TABLE CleaningSupplies (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  item_name STRING,
  quantity INT
)

CREATE TABLE DataCleansingSteps (
  step_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  step_description STRING
)

CREATE TABLE PreprocessedData (
  data_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  cleaned_data STRING,
  label INT
)

CREATE TABLE MLModelTrainingData (
  sample_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  features STRING,
  target_variable STRING
)

CREATE TABLE cleaning_users (
  user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  username VARCHAR(50),
  email VARCHAR(100),
  last_login TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE cleaning_orders (
  order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  order_date DATE,
  total_amount DECIMAL(10, 2)
)

CREATE TABLE cleaning_products (
  product_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  product_name VARCHAR(100),
  price DECIMAL(10, 2),
  category VARCHAR(50)
)

CREATE TABLE cleaning_reviews (
  review_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  product_id INT,
  rating INT,
  review_text TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE cleaning_logs (
  log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  log_date TIMESTAMP,
  log_message TEXT,
  log_type VARCHAR(50)
)
